title: Natural Alternatives: Fiscal 3Q Earnings Snapshot
text:
CARLSBAD, Calif. (AP) _ Natural Alternatives International Inc. (NAII) on Monday reported fiscal third-quarter net income of $2.1 million.
On a per-share basis, the Carlsbad, California-based company said it had net income of 30 cents.
The nutritional supplements manufacturer posted revenue of $31.8 million in the period.
Natural Alternatives shares have increased slightly more than 2 percent since the beginning of the year. In the final minutes of trading on Monday, shares hit $10.55, a climb of 8 percent in the last 12 months.
